show.description: Too Heavy to Handle is a dramatic revenge saga that follows Priya, a woman mocked and betrayed for her weight, who transforms into the fierce and confident Avni to reclaim her dignity and bring down those who wronged her. Blending emotion, transformation, and empowerment, the show is a rollercoaster of heartbreak, healing, and high-stakes drama.
